description.content:
Greetings!


We are a team of dedicated professionals focused on providing clean, high-quality, and fully responsive designs. We specialize in Wix website redesign, Wix website design, and developing Wix websites, ensuring your site looks professional and works flawlessly.


Whether you need to build a Wix website or create a fully functional Wix eCommerce website, we will work with you to bring your ideas to life. With clear communication and attention to detail, we deliver sites tailored to meet your business needs.


Our Premium Services:

  • Custom wix site design
  • Full mobile optimization
  • Wix online store setup for ecommerce
  • site redesign to modernize and optimize your site
  • Migration of existing sites to wix
  • Revamp wix site to improve functionality
  • Custom slideshows and advanced visual/video integration
  • Integration of 3rd-party tools and features
  • Booking integration & selling online courses
  • Blog editing, design, and full site upgrades


Guarantee: 100% Money-Back Protection

If we do not deliver the promised services or outcomes, youll receive a full refund. "Your trust is important we make it risk-free for you."

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why choose wix or squarespace website ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Overall, wix and squarespace offers a user-friendly platform with design flexibility, extensive features, and robust support, making it a popular choice for individuals and businesses looking to create a simple, professional and functional website without extensive technical skills.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What sets me apart from other sellers of website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: My expertise, customization skills, and commitment to professional Squarespace design and optimization set me apart from other website sellers. I am a top-level legend with 90,000 points in the Wix Partner Program.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How much is your experience in website design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: With 7 years of experience in website design, I have successfully completed over 1500 Wix websites. My expertise in the field allows me to create stunning and functional websites that meet the unique needs of each client.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you customize templates?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, as a certified expert, I can customize the template and also create a brand-new design from scratch.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do I submit any questions prior to placing my order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can ask as many as you have before placing your order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is it possible to schedule a Zoom call for website consultation?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can connect virtually over Zoom for an exclusive, one-on-one website consultation and discussion tailored to your needs. Discover the possibilities, unleash your vision, and together, we'll craft a roadmap for an exceptional online presence.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do we get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: There must be a clear understanding of the project's size and scope. Typically, we will define this as the site's pages and their contents. We have pre-made gig packages available for order, but if these don't seem to fit your needs, send us a message!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to provide?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
You need to provide the following things to get started:
 1.  Access to your wix account
 2.  Logo and color scheme
 3.  Name of the pages
 4.  Written and pictorial content for the pages
 5.  A reference(sample/competitor) website

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I am afraid of sharing my account details?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will create a website on my own account and transfer it to you once it is complete, you may also add me as a contributor for redesign purposes.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you simply redesign my current website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes, I will redesign your existing website to make it better organized, user-friendly, easy to
navigate, both desktop and mobile responsive, and moreprofessional.
